She always felt slightly awkward referring to Greek deities in her common speech, she acknowledged that the Greek deities were gods, but preferred to steer clear of them. It seemed like a mutual agreement, because they kept clear of her too. As a general rule, the few Greek immortals that she had met had not liked her at all, and she the same. However, she was constantly among people that worshipped them, so perhaps speaking more like them was not a bad thing.<br>
